@node Overview
@chapter Overview

@samp{outline-extras.el} extends the built-in @samp{outline} library with improved heading promotion and demotion commands. The built-in @code{outline-promote} and @code{outline-demote} commands, when called with a prefix argument, operate on the entire subtree but leave point at an unintuitive position afterward. The commands in this package wrap those operations so that point reliably returns to the heading line you just modified, making repeated promotions and demotions smoother.

The package requires only @samp{outline} itself and works in any buffer where @samp{outline-minor-mode} or a derived mode (such as @samp{org-mode}) is active.

